{"tid":1687541,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"謝霆鋒澳門搞搖滾美食節　師弟師妹齊撐","createTime":"2019-11-02T02:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T03:57:56.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d58af93bcf47ba11700bee4b8b4a2180aa5570c","tid":1687541,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒將於11月30日至12月1日，一連兩日於澳門舉辦首個大型音樂美食盛會「鋒味搖滾美食節」，集合音樂力量，霆鋒除了重拾結他再次搖滾，他更率領一眾師弟師妹容祖兒、羅力威、許靖韻及劉郡格同台演出。另外還有樂隊Mr.、王灝兒（JW）及新加坡歌手董姿彥等獻唱，澳門人氣組合MFM一同勁歌熱舞。除此之外，現場更有著名亞洲人氣音樂製作人及DJ Corsak打碟，以勁強音樂動感與觀眾打成一片。<br />\n除了音樂表演，曾在《鋒味》節目中憑高超廚藝脫穎而出的鋒廚隊伍更會現身搖滾美食節，與一眾主廚進行烹飪交流，更即席創作多款創新菜式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191016/photo/bkn-20191016160711681-1016_00862_001_02p.jpg?20191016160816\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191016%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191016160711681-1016_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20191016160816&h=cfd434f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191016/photo/bkn-20191016160711681-1016_00862_001_03p.jpg?20191016160816\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191016%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191016160711681-1016_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20191016160816&h=4ef151d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191016/photo/bkn-20191016160711681-1016_00862_001_04p.jpg?20191016160816\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191016%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191016160711681-1016_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20191016160816&h=7fe966a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191016/photo/bkn-20191016160711681-1016_00862_001_05p.jpg?20191016160816\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191016%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191016160711681-1016_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20191016160816&h=fecc0386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98f12f2e6f1dcb7abc698fc46689ff3173fe6966","tid":1687541,"uid":43816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afa578018029b9aaab001336b9c775855c655a3","tid":1687541,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"煮結他？"},{"pid":"a4cddd90e316c14f938d50e46eb01f0a93a99c3e","tid":1687541,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7afa578018029b9aaab001336b9c775855c655a3","tid":1687541,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"煮結他？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"彈意粉"},{"pid":"2745893175bc482a91e07f5a33e6e189b908c1d1","tid":1687541,"uid":287792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"唔L使錢啊"},{"pid":"70c9d74596acae1978e7160d39d9251856204f75","tid":1687541,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYzJAWY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYzJAWY.gif&h=a0d111a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e99117975ca31eb89a3d71191601370b99035839","tid":1687541,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"愛國親建制搖滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}